# game/dialogue/script-ch30-idles.rpy:2165
translate ptbr idle_36_6f02ab5b:

    # y "I really like having these types of conversations with you, you know. Silly little things."
    y ""

# game/dialogue/script-ch30-idles.rpy:2173
translate ptbr idle_36_flight_a1c6ad8b:

    # y "The ability to fly, huh? We could soar through the skies together and take in so many majestic views."
    y ""

# game/dialogue/script-ch30-idles.rpy:2175
translate ptbr idle_36_flight_ba49cadb:

    # y "We could sit atop mountains and go all over the world together. That would be nice."
    y ""

# game/dialogue/script-ch30-idles.rpy:2176
translate ptbr idle_36_flight_74f49263:

    # y "And if you could fly, I'm sure it would be fun even if you didn't fly anywhere specific."
    y ""

# game/dialogue/script-ch30-idles.rpy:2177
translate ptbr idle_36_flight_fd1fa027:

    # y "Just zooming around in the air would be incredible, wouldn't it?"
    y ""

# game/dialogue/script-ch30-idles.rpy:2180
translate ptbr idle_36_flight_4c02cd61:

    # y "F-flight eh..?"
    y ""

# game/dialogue/script-ch30-idles.rpy:2181
translate ptbr idle_36_flight_2867d144:

    # y "I'm not too sure what you would use that for..."
    y ""

# game/dialogue/script-ch30-idles.rpy:2183
translate ptbr idle_36_flight_b58216dc:

    # y "I-I don't know if I would be up for such a thing with you..."
    y ""

# game/dialogue/script-ch30-idles.rpy:2184
translate ptbr idle_36_flight_6b32812f:

    # y "I wouldn't be that good at it anyway."
    y ""

# game/dialogue/script-ch30-idles.rpy:2186
translate ptbr idle_36_flight_5bb04faa:

    # y "What if... what if you decided to use that as an excuse to just leave me behind? I-I honestly don't see that as being too far-fetched."
    y ""

# game/dialogue/script-ch30-idles.rpy:2187
translate ptbr idle_36_flight_d4be9076:

    # y "I mean, what would I be to deserve a flight with you? With such an ability you'd probably be better off somewhere else, without me... doing anything you wanted."
    y ""

# game/dialogue/script-ch30-idles.rpy:2189
