    # y "O-or what if you dropped me?"
    y ""

# game/dialogue/script-ch30-idles.rpy:2190
translate ptbr idle_36_flight_71a86863:

    # y "..."
    y ""

# game/dialogue/script-ch30-idles.rpy:2192
translate ptbr idle_36_flight_fb5f16a5:

    # y "Oh... I'm sorry... It was really rude of me to accuse you of such things. Let's just move onto something else... Sorry about that."
    y ""

# game/dialogue/script-ch30-idles.rpy:2193
translate ptbr idle_36_flight_333c32cc:

    # y "That is, if that matters at all..."
    y ""

# game/dialogue/script-ch30-idles.rpy:2201
translate ptbr idle_36_invis_cad60767:

    # y "Invisibility, huh? I noticed that a lot of people who choose that ability seem to... well..."
    y ""

# game/dialogue/script-ch30-idles.rpy:2203
translate ptbr idle_36_invis_76ad2df6:

    # y "They want to use it to slip into places they really shouldn't be, or to spy on people. Like going into locker rooms... or bathrooms..."
    y ""

# game/dialogue/script-ch30-idles.rpy:2205
translate ptbr idle_36_invis_811da557:

    # y "A-Are you trying to spy on me at times like that, [player]?"
    y ""

# game/dialogue/script-ch30-idles.rpy:2206
translate ptbr idle_36_invis_94f8a51f:

    # y "I'm not sure I'd like that... Someone watching me without permission."
    y ""

# game/dialogue/script-ch30-idles.rpy:2208
translate ptbr idle_36_invis_9ea67376:

    # y "Like when I'm in the shower or changing! Oh God, how embarrassing... b-but, uh..."
